invalid type: string "Ludhiana Industrial Fire — Hosiery Supplier Destroyed (2022). Fire gutted a major hosiery supplier's manufacturing unit in Ludhiana's focal point industrial area. Complete loss of production capacity. Supplier unable to fulfil any POs. Affected regions: Ludhiana, Punjab. Affected routes: Road freight Ludhiana to Delhi NCR, Road freight Ludhiana to Mumbai.", expected f64oole